
Overview of adj talkative

The adj talkative has 3 senses (first 1 from tagged texts)
                                       
1. (1) chatty, gabby, garrulous, loquacious, talkative, talky -- (full of trivial conversation; "kept from her housework by gabby neighbors")
2. bigmouthed, blabbermouthed, blabby, talkative -- (unwisely talking too much)
3. expansive, talkative -- (friendly and open and willing to talk; "wine made the guest expansive")
